The young women will have an opportunity to ride on a boat at this activity.
For this part of the activity, parents must fill out and sign a permission and medical release form.
There are two options:

1. Parents can drop of their children at the activity and complete the form then.
2. Parents can send their young women to the activity with completed forms.  The form can be found here: [link](https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/callings/church-safety-and-health/permission-and-medical-release-form?lang=eng).
Parents: please remember this if your young women will be carpooling.

We repeat: this form must be completed for each young woman who
wants to ride the boat.

